<h1>Pages#home</h1>

<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://www.coworker.com/mag/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/theworkprojectatmidtownsoundwillplazaiihongkong.jpg);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Le Co-hemps  for <strong>creative people</strong>!</h1>
